{"tid":1367841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[太古地產咩事?] 喺太古站出面開咗嗰連儂牆，唔夠半個鐘就俾人拆咗","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:18:00.000Z","uid":223593,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61309a7540e7d20ba87fd4cc763f68e513eb55de","tid":1367841,"uid":223593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱我喺太古站D出口出面開咗嗰連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqOswGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqOswGL.jpg&h=99557f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太古城中心嘅職員同我講呢到私人地方<br />\n如果清潔嘅話就會拆走<br />\n我本來以為佢地最快都係聽日先會拆<br />\n點知過咗半個鐘都無 佢地就拆走曬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XbLeV8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbLeV8x.jpg&h=65ffd08d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n使唔使咁驚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我揀嗰度係因為人流多同埋對面有間酒店，可以俾啲外國人了解吓<br />\n請問各位太古嗰頭仲有無咩公共地方可以貼?<br />\n以我所知 有就有不過無乜人流<br />\nP.S. 唔該曬啱啱嗰位幫我手嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76bf7a88bf2597b3e09f2d1ffb3aa12c6fb32ad","tid":1367841,"uid":44870,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"唔清係人情, 清係道理"},{"pid":"faec60898a4507bd2e5e79af7ab4fdb027c46dfa","tid":1367841,"uid":165683,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:05:07.000Z","msg":"太古自己人唔好搞 Please"},{"pid":"13c31250c82e76fd104ded7cc9c65745875f585d","tid":1367841,"uid":78947,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"咁真係私人地方麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a74980e9fc111695347cc49c724af537cf5b48c","tid":1367841,"uid":267290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"條j蝗住邊，痴係佢個個度"},{"pid":"c550c7fb3b584b8474ee99b7826bf8c3e3b041db","tid":1367841,"uid":223593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e76bf7a88bf